Progetica,is,an,Italian,financial,consulting,firm,based,in,Milan,They,engage,in,activities,such,as,financial,education,tools,development,and,the,diffusion,of,information,via,newspapers,websites,books,etc,The,Progetica,website,is,offered,in,both,Italian,and,English,The,Progetica,SOAP,API,allows,users,to,retrieve,informational,slides,from,the,website,These,slides,cover,topics,such,as,portfolio,analysis,mortgages,and,pensions